name: Hector Cushion
description:
Hector is hand screen printed in chocolate ink, with coral contrast details on a square buttercream 100% cotton cushion with color matched zip closure.  Comes complete with cushion insert, ready to be used.

All our products are made using hand cut stencils and hand screen printed, please note the colors and image placement may vary slightly from product images.  Each product is unique.

We only use water-based inks for a soft feel; please hand wash separately in cold water.

Approximate dimensions:
16” wide x 16” high
41cm wide x 41cm high

Hector is made and ready to be dispatched within 1 week.

Order all three cushion designs for £60, enter 3CUSHIONS at checkout.
